day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20case%20was%20filed%20against%C2%A0the%20accused%20constable%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkangana-ranaut-slapped-chandigarh-airport-kulwinder-kaur-cisf-my-mother-was-at-farmers-protest-constable-who-slapped-kangana-ranaut-5832597%5C%22%3EKulwinder%20Kaur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20she%20was%20also%20suspended%20after%20she%20allegedly%20slapped%20Ms%20Ranaut%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20actor%20was%20on%20the%20way%20to%20board%20a%20flight%20to%20Delhi%20when%20the%20incident%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20paramilitary%20security%20personnel%20said%20she%20was%20triggered%20by%20an%20old%20statement%20from%20Ms%20Ranaut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20gave%20a%20statement...%20that%20farmers%20are%20sitting%20there%20for%C2%A0%E2%82%B9%C2%A0100.%20Will%20she%20go%20and%20sit%20there%3F%20My%20mother%20was%20sitting%20there%20and%20protesting%20when%20she%20gave%20this%20statement...%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20farmers'%20protest%20in%202020%20against%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%20passed%20by%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20height%20of%20a%20nationwide%20agitation%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20had%20remarked%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post%20that%20an%20elderly%20woman%20at%20a%20protest%20site%20was%20being%20paid%20Rs%20100%20to%20sit%20there.%20After%20facing%20widespread%20backlash%2C%20the%20actor%20deleted%20the%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%2C%20recorded%20by%20onlookers%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20the%20Mandi%20MP%20can%20be%20seen%20escorted%20to%20the%20security%20checkpoint%20where%20the%20incident%20occurred.%20However%2C%20as%20she%20reaches%20the%20area%2C%20an%20argument%20breaks%20out%20and%20she%20is%20then%20escorted%20away.%20The%20video%20does%20not%20capture%20the%20alleged%20slap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20actor%20took%20to%20X%20and%20shared%20a%20video%20message%20about%20what%