a%20decisive%20factor%20in%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20central%20government%20in%20India%20(after%20Lok%20Sabha%20election)%2C%20his%20namesake%2C%20playing%20for%20the%20USA%20cricket%20team%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%2C%20delivered%20an%20important%20contribution%20in%20the%20victory%20against%20Pakistan.%20Seeing%20the%20stocks%20of%20'Nitish%20Kumars'%20rise%2C%20the%20world%20of%20social%20media%20couldn't%20help%20but%20draw%20parallels%20between%20the%20cricket%20and%20political%20worlds%20at%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlaying%20for%20the%20USA%20in%20the%20team's%20second%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20Group%20A%20match%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20scored%20a%20crucial%2014-ball%2014%2C%20remaining%20unbeaten%20as%20the%20scores%20of%20both%20teams%20were%20tied%20(159%20each)%20in%2040%20overs%20of%20play%20in%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20important%20for%20Nitish%2C%20and%20his%20partner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Aaron%20Jones%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110944-aaron-jones-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAaron%20Jones%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20keep%20their%20nerves%20calm%20in%20the%20tricky%20run-chase%20and%20they%20did%20just%20what%20was%20required.%20Later%2C%20the%20Mumbai-born%20USA%20pacer%20Saurabh%20Netravalkar%20won%20his%20team%20the%20match%20in%20the%20Super%20Over%20with%20an%20exceptional%20bowling%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20played%20and%20important%20role%20in%20rewarding%20his%20team%2C%20USA%2C%20a%20historic%20T20%20World%20Cup%20win.%20The%20other%20Nitish%2C%20in%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20is%20seemingly%20playing%20a%20similar%20role%20in%20India's%20government%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Is%20USA's%20Nitish%20Kumar%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Scarborough%2C%20Ontario%20in%201994%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20hasn't%20only%20played%20cricket%20for%20the%20USA%20on%20the%20international%20circuit.%20His%20cricketing%20journey%20began%20while%20playing%20for%20Canada%20in%20various%20tournaments%2C%20including%20the%20Under%2015s%20and%20the%20Under-19%20World%20Cup%20qualifiers%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20is%20also%20the%20youngest%20player%20to%20debut%20for%20Canada%20in%20a%20first-class%20match%2C%20playing%20against%20Kenya%20in%202009%20and%20the%20second-youngest%20to%20feature%20in%20an%20ODI%20match.%20When%20Canada%20qualified%20for%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%202011%2C%20Nitish%20made%20global%20history%2C%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20player%20to%20play%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20tournament.%20He%20was%20Canada's%20top-scoring%20batter%20in%20the%20qualifying%20stage%2C%20aggregating%20370%20runs%2C%20including%202%20tons.%20He%20also%20bagged%208%20wickets%20in%20that%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20also%20did%20wonders%20for%20Canada%2C%20emerging%20as%20the%20second-highest%20run-scorer%20in%20the%20qualifying%20stage.%20In%20the%20qualifiers%2C%20he%20scored%2057%20runs%20in%2044%20balls%20against%20Papua%20New%20Guinea.%20He%20was%20part%20of%20the%20team%20in%20the%202014%20World%20Cup%20qualifiers%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2030%2C%20Nitish%20became%20the%20latest%20to%20appear%20in%20a%20T20%20World%20Cup%20for%20two%20countries%20on%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20Covid-19%2C%20%5Band%5D%20Toronto%20had%20one%20of%20the%20longest%20lockdowns%20in%20the%20world.%20There%20was%20nothing%20going%20on%20in%20terms%20of%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Nitish%20told%20ESPNcricinfo%20ahead%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20to%20be%20fair%2C%20I've%20always%20dreamt%20about%20playing%20cricket.%20And%20I'm%20someone%20that's%20100%25%20in%3B%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20do%2050-50.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20shift%20to%20the%20USA.%20Aged%2026%20back%20then%2C%20Kumar%20only%20wanted%20to%20continue%20playing%20cricket%20and%20the%20United%20States%20gave%20him%20the%20opportunity%20to%20do%20so.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20give%20up%20playing%20cricket.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20wait.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717738560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F9930ou98_nitish-kumar-usa-afp_625x300_07_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fn-usas-victory-over-pakistan-nitish-kumar-played-a-key-role-5836754%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20a%20USA%20batter%2C%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20his%20team's%20historic%20victory%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fn-usas-victory-over-pakistan-nitish-kumar-played-a-key-role-5836754%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fn-usas-victory-over-pakistan-nitish-kumar-played-a-key-role-5836754%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fn-usas-victory-over-pakistan-nitish-kumar-played-a-key-role-5836754%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arjan%20praises%20Chirag%20on%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20victory%20-%20Exl%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717738459000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110786027%2Cimgsize-53356.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Farjan-bajwa-on-chirag-paswans-victory-in-the-2024-lok-sabha-elections-he-has-always-maintained-his-composure-grit-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F110785950.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110785950.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActor%20Arjan%20Bajwa%20expressed%20immense%20pride%20in%20