e%2Fzelenskyy-to-address-french-parliament-after-d-day%2Farticleshow%2F110783378.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fzelenskyy-to-address-french-parliament-after-d-day%2Famp_articleshow%2F110783378.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fzelenskyy-to-address-french-parliament-after-d-day%2Famp_articleshow%2F110783378.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elections%20Results%20Out%3A%20What%20Is%20The%20Salary%20Of%20An%20MP%2C%20What%20Perks%20Do%20They%20Get%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20recently%20concluded%20its%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20a%20major%20event%20that%20saw%20citizens%20cast%20their%20votes.%20While%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20managed%20to%20cross%20the%20halfway%20mark%20with%20a%20tally%20of%20293%20seats%2C%20the%20Opposition%20alliance%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20delivered%20a%20strong%20performance%2C%20securing%20232%20seats.%20As%20the%20new%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20(MP)%20prepare%20to%20take%20their%20seats%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpa.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FUpdated%2520version%2520of%2520MSA%2520Act%2520and%2520rules%2520made%2520thereunder.pdf%5C%22%3Esalaries%20and%20perks%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20worth%20looking%20at.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EMP%3A%20Salaries%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAn%20MP%20earns%20a%20basic%20salary%20of%20%E2%82%B91%2C00%2C000%20per%20month.%C2%A0This%20figure%20was%20set%20after%20the%20recent%20pay%20hike%20in%202018%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20aligning%20their%20salaries%20with%20the%20inflation%20rates%20and%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20living.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EMPs%3A%20Allowances%20and%20Perks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EConstituency%20allowance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMPs%20receive%20%E2%82%B970%2C000%20per%20month%20as%20a%20constituency%20allowance%20%E2%80%93%20to%20cover%20expenses%20related%20to%20maintaining%20offices%20and%20engaging%20with%20constituents%20within%20their%20electoral%20regions.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EOffice%20expenses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20receives%20%E2%82%B960%2C000%20per%20month%20for%20office%20expenses%2C%20which%20includes%20costs%20for%20stationary%2C%20telecommunications%20staff%20salaries%20etc.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EDaily%20allowance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDuring%20parliamentary%20sessions%20and%20committee%20meetings%2C%20MPs%20are%20entitled%20to%20a%20daily%20allowance%20of%20%E2%82%B92%2C000%20to%20cover%20lodging%2C%20food%20and%20any%20other%20expenses%20while%20they%20are%20in%20the%20capital.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ETravel%20allowance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMPs%20are%20entitled%20to%2034%20free%20domestic%20air%20journeys%20per%20year%20for%20themselves%20and%20their%20immediate%20families.%20They%20also%20receive%20free%20first-class%20train%20travel%20for%20official%20and%20personal%20purposes.%20MPs%20can%20also%20claim%20mileage%20allowances%20when%20travelling%20by%20road%20within%20their%20constituencies.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EHousing%20and%20accommodation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMPs%20are%20given%20rent-free%20accommodations%20in%20prime%20areas%20during%20their%205-year%20term.%20Depending%20on%20seniority%2C%20they%20may%20receive%20bungalows%2C%20flats%20or%20hostel%20rooms.%20Those%20who%20choose%20not%20to%20use%20the%20official%20accommodation%20can%20claim%20a%20housing%20allowance%20of%20%E2%82%B92%2C00%2C000%20per%20month.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EMedical%20facilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMPs%20and%20their%20immediate%20families%20are%20entitled%20to%20free%20medical%20care%20under%20the%20Central%20Government%20Health%20Scheme%20(CGHS).%20This%20includes%20treatment%20at%20government%20hospitals%20and%20select%20private%20hospitals%20which%20come%20under%20the%20scheme.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPension%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFormer%20MPs%20receive%20a%20pension%20of%20%E2%82%B925%2C000%20per%20month%20after%20serving%20one%20term%20in%20Parliament.%20For%20every%20extra%20year%20of%20service%2C%20they%20get%20an%20increment%20of%20%E2%82%B92%2C000%20per%20month.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPhone%20and%20internet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMPs%20are%20allotted%20up%20to%201%2C50%2C000%20free%20telephone%20calls%20annually.%20They%20also%20receive%20free%20high-speed%20internet%20connections%20at%20their%20residences%20and%20offices.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWater%20and%20electricity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMPs%20are%20provided%20with%20free%20electricity%20up%20to%2050%2C000%20units%20and%20free%20water%20up%20to%204%2C000%20kilolitres%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717732500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fum6j1rso_new-parliament-building_625x300_19_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-all-about-salaries-perks-of-members-of-parliament-5831798%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MPs%20are%20given%20rent-free%20accommodations%20in%20prime%20areas%20during%20their%205-year%20term.%20Depending%20on%20seniority%2C%20they%20may%20receive%20bungalows%2C%20flats%20or%20hostel%20rooms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-all-about-salaries-perks-of-members-of-parliament-5831798%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-all-about-salaries-perks-of-members-of-parliament-5831798%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news