itle%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Maharashtra%3A%20A%20Lesson%20For%20Assembly%20Polls%20Against%20'Jod-Tod'%20Politics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Fqr2q5ltg_sharad-pawar-uddhav-press-conference-pti-650_650x400_24_November_19.jpg%3Fim%3DResize%3D(1230%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Felections%2Fmaharashtra-state-lok-sabha-election-results-2024%5C%22%3ELok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20from%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20another%20political%20churn%20in%20the%20state%20before%20the%20assembly%20polls%20due%20in%20October%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Felections%2Fmaharashtra-state-lok-sabha-election-results-2024%5C%22%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Congress%20would%20like%20to%20believe%20it%20was%20a%20test%20of%20Brand%20Modi's%20popularity%2C%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-election-results-day-lok-sabha-results-live-in-maharashtra-ogs-uddhav-thackeray-sharad-pawar-stand-tall-5814326%5C%22%3Efour%20regional%20parties%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20born%20out%20of%20splits%20in%20their%20mother%20organisations%2C%20it%20was%20always%20about%20settling%20legacy%20issues%20and%20asserting%20dominance%20before%20the%20real%20battle%20begins%20for%20the%20control%20of%20an%20industrialised%2C%20cash-rich%20state%20that%20is%20home%20to%20the%20country's%20financial%20capital%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20wealthiest%20civic%20body%2C%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Inevitable%20Verdict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20nearly%20four%20decades%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20-%20now%20split%20into%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Shinde)%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fuddhav-thackeray-is-not-joining-nda-sharad-pawar-s-ncp-800612%5C%22%3EUddhav%20Bal%20Thackeray%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20UBT)%2C%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar)%20and%20NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar)%20-%20have%20been%20the%20pivots%20on%20which%20Maharashtra%20politics%20turns.%20After%20two%20years%20of%20dramatic%20twists%20and%20turns%20in%20both%20parties%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20change%20of%20government%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20an%20ugly%20division%20in%20Maharashtra's%20political%20first%20family%20(the%20Pawars)%2C%20and%20Eknath%20Shinde%20from%20outside%20the%20bloodline%20laying%20claim%20to%20Bal%20Thackeray's%20bequest%2C%20it%20was%20inevitable%20that%20the%20soap%20operas%20playing%20out%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20NCP%20would%20shape%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20results%20that%20the%20sympathy%20factor%20weighed%20heavily%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20voters%20as%20they%20gave%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20combo%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20the%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar)%20and%20the%20Congress%20the%20majority%20of%20the%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Maharashtra.%20The%20NCP%20(Sharad%20Pawar)%20won%20eight%20of%20the%2010%20seats%20it%20contested%2C%20the%20Sena%20(UBT)%20bagged%20nine%20of%20the%2021%20it%20fought%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20stunned%20by%20emerging%20as%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20alliance%20with%2013%20seats%20out%20of%20the%2017%20assigned%20to%20it.%20That's%20a%20grand%20total%20of%2030%20of%20Maharashtra's%2048%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fuddhav-not-joining-bjp-led-nda-working-to-install-maha-vikas-aghadi-govt-ncp-sp-leader-5832333%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Uddhav%20Thackeray%20Is%20Not%20Joining%20NDA%3A%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20only%20managed%2017%20seats.%20The%20party%20was%20the%20worst%20sufferer%20as%20its%20tally%20fell%20to%20just%20nine%20from%20the%2023%20it%20won%20in%202019.%20Shinde's%20Sena%20bagged%20seven%20seats%20out%20of%20the%2014%20it%20contested%2C%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20got%20just%20one%20seat%20from%20the%20five%20it%20fought%20in.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20the%20Shinde%20Sena's%20strike%20rate%20is%20more%20impressive%20than%20that%20of%20its%20rival%20UBT%20faction%2C%20it%20was%20the%20battle%20in%20the%20six%20seats%20of%20Mumbai%20that%20has%20settled%20the%20bitterly%20contested%20emotive%20legacy%20question%20of%20which%20is%20the%20real%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan't%20Ride%20On%20Sympathy%20Alone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20is%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20founded%20by%20Bal%20Thackeray%20and%20has%20been%20the%20fiefdom%20of%20the%20united%20party%20for%20over%20three%20decades.%20The%20results%20prove%20that%20Brand%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20not%20the%20usurper%2C%20reigns%20supreme%20on%20his%20father's%20home%20turf.%20The%20Sena%20(UBT)%20won%20three%20of%20the%20four%20seats%20it%20contested%20and%20helped%20its%20ally%20Congress%20win%20one.%20The%20BJP%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20just%20one%20seat%20-%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal's%20Mumbai%20North%20-%20while%20Shinde's%20Sena%20scraped%20through%20in%20the%20remaining%20seat%20by%20a%20meagre%2048%20votes%20that%20came%20through%20postal%20ballots%20right%20at%20the%20end%20in%20a%20nail-biting%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20parties%20regroup%20for%20the%20upcoming%20battle%20to%20control%20Maharashtra%2C%20several%20other%20factors%20will%20come%20into%20play.%20After%20all%2C%20sympathy%20cannot%20be%20a%20permanent%20mood%20among%20voters.%20The%20BJP%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20will%20have%20to%20introspect%20why%20it%20lost%20so%20badly%20in%20its%20strongholds%20of%20Vidarbha%20and%20Marathwada%2C%20that%20too%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20left%20virtually%20headless%20after%20an%20exodus%20of%20leaders%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20including%20former%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Chavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-pawar-says-he-takes-full-responsibility-for-ncps-poor-performance-5835724%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0On%20Wife's%20Baramati%20Defeat%20To%20Cousin%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20Says%20This%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgrarian%20distress%20has%20been%20rampant%20in%20these%20areas%20for%20several%20years%20and%20the%20Modi%20government's%20flip-flops%20on%20agricultural%20policies%20deepened%20anger%20among%20farmers.%20It%20is%20also%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20lost%20much%20of%20its%20Dalit%20base%20in%20these%20regions%20following%20the%20Opposition-stoked%20controversy%20over%20plans%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution.%20Maharashtra%20is%20the%20home%20state%20of%20the%20writer%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20and%20with%20Dalits%20forming%2010.5%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population%2C%20any%20perceived%20attack%20on%20Ambedkar's%20masterpiece%20was%20bound%20to%20alienate%20them.%20The%20BJP%20has%20paid%20a%20heavy%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20was%20the%20running%20controversy%20over%20the%20Maratha%20demand%20for%20OBC%20status%20and%20accompanying%20reservation%20benefits.%20The%20delay%20in%20bringing%20a%2010%25%20quota%20for%20Marathas%20hurt%20the%20BJP%20and%20Shinde's%20Sena%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP.%20Being%20partners%20in%20government%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20latter%20were%20seen%20as%20collaborators%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20deny%20reservation%20benefits%20to%20Marathas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20BJP%20tried%20to%20stoke%20communal%20sentiments%20with%20an%20aggressive%20campaign%20against%20'love%20jihad'%2C%20voters%20seemed%20as%20unmoved%20by%20this%20as%20they%20were%20by%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAjit%20Pawar's%20humiliation%20at%20the%20hustings%20has%20settled%20the%20vexed%20issue%20long%20rocking%20the%20family%20of%20who%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20political%20heir%20is.%20His%20daughter%2C%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20can%20now%20firmly%20claim%20the%20mantle%20even%20as%20Ajit%20Pawar%20will%20have%20to%20contemplate%20his%20next%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Answer%20To%20The%20Legacy%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legacy%20issue%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%20also%20been%20settled%20in%20favour%20of%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%20Analysts%20in%20Maharashtra%20foresee%20a%20run%20on%20Shinde's%20party%20and%20predict%20that%20many%20of%20his%20MLAs%20could%20go%20back%20to%20join%20Uddhav's%20faction.%20With%20assembly%20elections%20merely%20months%20away%2C%20desperation%20must%20be%20rising.%20Apparently%2C%20some%20of%20those%20leaders%20have%20already%20sent%20feelers%20to%20the%20Sena%20(UBT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20the%20BJP%20that%20has%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20drawing%20board%20as%20it%20reviews%20the%20ruins%20of%20the%20strategy%20it%20crafted%20in%202022%20to%20snatch%20the%20government%20from%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20by%20breaking%20his%20party%20and%20later%20splitting%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP.%20Will%20it%20try%20to%20woo%20Uddhav%20back%20by%20dangling%20the%20carrot%20of%20restoring%20to%20him%20the%20coveted%20Shiv%20Sena%20election%20symbol%2C%20currently%20with%20the%20Shinde%20faction%2C%20and%20certain%20properties%20that%20are%20currently%20the%20subject%20of%20dispute%20between%20the%20two%20factions%3F%20Or%20will%20it%20heed%20the%20punishment%20meted%20out%20by%20voters%20to%20the%20politics%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ejod-