22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Frbi-mpc-meeting-live-rbi-monetary-policy-latest-when-and-where-to-watch-the-governor-s-shaktikanta-das-announcement-124060700114_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Frbi-mpc-meeting-live-rbi-monetary-policy-latest-when-and-where-to-watch-the-governor-s-shaktikanta-das-announcement-124060700114_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Frbi-mpc-meeting-live-rbi-monetary-policy-latest-when-and-where-to-watch-the-governor-s-shaktikanta-das-announcement-124060700114_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Babar%20Azam%20Minces%20No%20Words%20After%20Embarrassing%20Loss%20To%20USA%2C%20Blames...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20captain%20Babar%20Azam%20opened%20up%20about%20their%20shortcomings%20and%20revealed%20the%20turning%20point%20of%20the%20game%20as%20they%20slumped%20to%20an%20early%20upset%20against%20the%20USA%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20In%20a%20nail-biting%20thriller%20that%20kept%20the%20fans%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20their%20seats%2C%20USA%20pulled%20off%20a%20remarkable%20win%20over%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20Super%20Over.%20Pakistan%20were%20reeling%20at%2026%2F3%20when%20Babar%20and%20Shadab%20Khan%20joined%20hands%20at%20the%20crease.%20The%20duo%20stabilised%20their%20sinking%20ship%20by%20forging%20a%20promising-looking%2072-run%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20Babar-led%20team%20again%20found%20themselves%20in%20turmoil%20after%20Shadab%20failed%20to%20sweep%20it%20over%20short%20fine%20leg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20six%20overs%2C%20the%20ball%20was%20holding%20and%20was%20swinging.%20But%20the%20more%20partnerships%20we%20build%2C%20the%20better%20for%20us.%20When%20Shadab%20and%20I%20started%20the%20partnership%2C%20we%20got%20momentum.%20I%20think%20when%20we%20lost%20the%20wickets%20back-to-back%2C%20that%20was%20the%20turning%20point.%20When%20you%20got%20momentum%2C%20you%20lost%20it%20because%20of%20losing%20wickets%2C%26quot%3B%20Babar%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfamiliar%20conditions%20against%20a%20USA%20side%20that%20the%20Pakistan%20team%20was%20unacquainted%20played%20a%20prominent%20role%20in%20their%20downfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20batters%20struggled%20to%20spend%20time%20on%20the%20field%20and%20the%20pacers%20didn't%20find%20their%20rhythm.%20The%20fielders%20ended%20up%20giving%20away%20misfields%20that%20never%20allowed%20the%20USA%20to%20feel%20pressure%20until%20the%20final%20three%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBabar%20didn't%20hold%20back%20while%20assessing%20their%20performance%20in%20all%20three%20departments%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20playing%20good%20in%20all%20three%20departments.%20We%20are%20better%20than%20that%20in%20the%20bowling%2C%20we%20are%20not%20in%20the%20first%20six%20overs%20taking%20wickets.%20In%20the%20middle%20overs%20your%20spinner%20is%20not%20taking%20wickets%20then%20pressure%20is%20on%20us.%20But%20I%20think%20the%20way%20they%20finished%20the%20game%20in%20the%20super%20overs%20I%20think%20credit%20to%20the%20US%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Babar%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20difficult%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20but%20we%20covered%20it.%20But%20as%20a%20professional%2C%20you%20have%20to%20step%20up%20against%20such%20a%20performance%20or%20such%20a%20team%20in%20the%20batting%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20order.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20excuse%20that%20they%20played%20well.%20I%20think%20we%20played%20badly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20succumbing%20to%20an%20unprecedented%20defeat%2C%20the%20Pakistan%20skipper%20acknowledged%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bfeeling%20good%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20am%20feeling%20good.%20If%20you%20lose%20a%20match%2C%20you%20are%20always%20upset.%20I%20think%20we%20are%20not%20playing%20well%2C%20on%20both%20sides.%20Fielding%2C%20bowling%2C%20and%20batting%2C%26quot%3B%20Babar%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20game%2C%20Pakistan%20managed%20to%20crawl%20to%20159%2F7%20after%20Shaheen%20Afridi%20came%20in%20and%20pulled%20off%20a%20couple%20of%20big%20hits%20at%20the%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%2C%20the%20USA%20looked%20well%20poised%20to%20chase%20down%20the%20total.%20After%20Andries%20Gous%20and%20the%20captain%20Monank%20Patel%20brought%20up%20a%2068-run%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Pakistan%20made%20inroads%20of%20a%20comeback%20with%20the%20pacers%20hitting%20consistent%20line%20and%20length.%20With%20five%20needed%20on%20the%20final%20ball%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%20struck%20a%20four%20to%20send%20the%20game%20to%20Super%20Over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperienced%20quick%20Mohammad%20Amir%20who%20shined%20in%20the%20penultimate%20over%20was%20handed%20the%20ball%20to%20bowl%20the%20final%20six%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20complete%20contrast%20in%20performance%2C%20he%20missed%20his%20line%2C%20bowled%20a%20couple%20of%20wides%20and%20gave%20away%2018%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%2C%20Pakistan%20folded%20on%2013%2F1%20and%20allowed%20the%20USA%20to%20walk%20away%20with%20a%205-run%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717731300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ftc231dr8_babar-azam-_625x300_07_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Ft20-world-cup-blunt-babar-azam-reveals-exact-reason-behind-pakistans-embarrassing-defeat-to-usa-5835628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20succumbing%20to%20an%20unprecedented%20def