ed%20or%20monogrammed.%C2%A0Duh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bdf0dd35-64c3-440d-b42f-f21b8a967e5a%5C%22%3EFor%20many%20families%20with%20disposable%20income%2C%20outsourcing%20is%20the%20solution%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeth%20Leffel%2C%20a%20Boca%20Raton%20mother%2C%20turned%20to%20Denny's%2C%20a%20children's%20boutique%20with%20stores%20in%20New%20York%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20Florida%2C%20the%20first%20summer%20she%20sent%20her%20daughter%20to%20camp%2C%20she%20told%20The%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20boutique%20boasts%20personal%20shoppers%20who%20work%20one-on-one%20with%20families%2C%20going%20item%20by%20item%20on%20each%20packing%20list%20to%20supply%20the%20necessary%20goods.%20Spencer%20Klein%2C%20whose%20family%20owns%20the%20business%2C%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20the%20average%20first-time%20camper%20spends%20anywhere%20from%20%241%2C500%20to%20%242%2C000%20at%20Denny's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dropping%20about%20%242%2C000%20at%20Denny's%20and%20%24250%20at%20Party%20City%20the%20first%20year%2C%20Lefell%20told%20the%20outlet%20she%20now%20searches%20for%20deals%20and%20dupes%20of%20more%20expensive%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22summer%20camp%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f469d1442f43f001ddff325%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20Barwick%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENatalie%20Liberman%2C%20another%20Boca%20Raton-based%20mom%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F06%2F23%2Fparents-spend-up-to-5k-getting-kids-cool-for-summer-camp%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20that%20she%20spent%20nearly%20%245%2C000%20making%20sure%20her%20seven-year-old%20daughter%20was%20set%20with%20rainbow%20merch%20and%20monogrammed%20clothing%20items%20ahead%20of%20summer%20camp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPers