%3E.%20It%20is%20here%20that%20the%20roots%20of%20Doon%20Gooseberry%20Farm%20run%20deep%2C%20where%20our%20dedication%20to%20purity%20and%20quality%20is%20firm.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20use%20shells%20of%20organic%20eggs%2C%20vegetable%20peels%2C%20and%20cow%20manure%20as%20the%20prime%20source%20of%20nourishment%20for%20their%20cultivation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201455px)%20100vw%2C%201455px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAmla-trees-at-the-farm_11zon-1717158064.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221455%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20amla%20(gooseberry)%20trees%20lining%20the%20farm.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAmla-trees-at-the-farm_11zon-1717158064.jpg%201455w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAmla-trees-at-the-farm_11zon-1717158064-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAmla-trees-at-the-farm_11zon-1717158064-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAmla-trees-at-the-farm_11zon-1717158064-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAmla-trees-at-the-farm_11zon-1717158064-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351732%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221092%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20amla%20(gooseberry)%20trees%20lining%20the%20farm.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20journey%20has%20been%20far%20from%20smooth.%20%E2%80%9CWater%20availability%20is%20a%20critical%20issue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Namita%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBeing%20in%20a%20hilly%20area%20with%20a%20non-perennial%20river%20nearby%2C%20water%20scarcity%20is%20a%20significant%20challenge.%20This%20is%20a%20primary%20reason%20why%20many%20peop